Dear {!conname}, <br></br><br></br>
        
In order for us to re-register you to work with Blue Arrow we need you to provide some information. Once these have been completed we will be in touch to move to the next stage in the process.
<br></br>
Please click on the links below to complete:<Br></Br>

<br></br><div style="font-size:13px;">
<apex:outputLink styleClass="linkunderline" rendered="{!dec = False}" value="{!Decalartion}"
id="theLink02">• <b>Declarations</b> <br></br></apex:outputLink> 

<apex:outputLink styleClass="linkunderline" rendered="{!portwcount123 = TRUE}"  value="{!RightToWork}"
